Project Details -
Retrofit library used for network call
Data get consume form "https://jsonplaceholder.typicode.com/albums"
By defualt list get sorted bt Title(Alphabetically)
Sort by Title and Sort by Id option provided in menu
pull down refresh data option added

Project future reference -
Data can be save offline with help of sqlite or Online by firebase cloud db
Details sharing option can be added to share data over mail or whatsapp
Login option can be added with help of 3rd party api login (Google,Facebook)
